# 📉 Customer Churn Analysis with Excel & Power BI

Analyze customer churn behavior using real data and visualize key insights through a dynamic Power BI dashboard.

---

## 🧾 Dataset Overview

Includes details on:
- Customer demographics
- Subscription & service usage
- Charges (monthly & total)
- Churn status (Yes/No)

📂 File: `Customer_Churn_Analysis.xlsx`

---

## 🎯 Project Goals

✔️ Understand what drives customer churn  
✔️ Segment churn vs. loyal customers  
✔️ Visualize churn metrics interactively  
✔️ Support smarter retention decisions  

---

## 🔍 Sample Insights

- High monthly charges → higher churn  
- Tech support absence → more churn  
- Fiber optic users churn more than DSL  
- Long-tenure users show higher loyalty  

---

## 📊 Tools Used

- **Microsoft Excel** – for cleaning & prep  
- **Power BI** – for dashboard visualization  
- **Power Query** – for transforming data  
- **DAX** – for KPIs & logic-based visuals  

